Field.Name: Consent
Field.PromptText: This information is being collected in order to assist emergency response and healthcare personnel in the following tasks: protecting the health and safety of workers, administering present or future care, and understanding and improving emergency response operations. By providing this information, the worker consents to the collection, use, and maintenance of personal data. Information may be shared with incident command staff or other parties as permitted or required by law.

Field.Name: Active
Field.PromptText: Active (worker may be considered for possible future deployment)

Field.Name: ActiveInstructions
Field.PromptText: Check this box if the worker is currently affiliated with the organization and has not retired.

Field.Name: Deployable
Field.PromptText: Deployable (worker is currently available for deployment)

Field.Name: DeployableInstructions
Field.PromptText: Check this box if the worker is fit for, and consents to, possible future deployment.
